hey this weekend was so much fun! i had a soccer game saturday n we wont 3-1 woo hoo! n then chelsea, sam, karley all came over n we went out to eat at hooligans n then went home n went bike riding to go c the cows cuz they r all so cute! n then we went home n sam, karley, n chelsea were all like attacking me n holdin me down n then karley would stick her naked butt in my face lol it was so nasty. ya n then we went outside n put up a tent in my yard n put a whole bunch of blankets in there. n then ian wanted to hang out w/ us so he came over around like 9 n we hung out in the tent for a couple hours n then he went home n then we came inside n watched white chicks n then fell alseep. then sunday morning chelsea woke up which woke me up lol n then we both woke up sam n karley n then we made ourselves breakfast n then we rode our bikes to this big humungous dirt pile that u can get to by my neighborhood n this path thingy behing troys house. but this time there was a big fence around the whole thing so chelsea started digging a little hole under the fence n they all squeezed under it but lol they r alot tinier than me so lol i had a little trouble gettin my butt under the fence lol n they were all tryn to help me n it was so hilarious! but i finally got thru n we stayed there for like 20 min n then left n this time i just climbed over the fence lol. then we got home we wanted to go for a picnic so we packed all of our food in a basket lol n then we went n ate it at this constrution house across the street from my house n we ate it upstairs. n then when we were eating we heard a guys voice n so we got scared that we were goin to get in trouble cuz we thought it was the worker ppl or somethn lol n so we packed everything up n there is no way down cuz the ppl r down stairs n we r upstairs so there was no where to go so sam starts climbing out the window thinking she was goin to jump but we were really high up so lol she was like freaking out haha n so then she wants to get back up so chelsea n karley r helping her bak up n we were trying to be quiet so that the ppl wouldnt here us but i was laughing so hard at sam omg it was so funny!! that was definatly the funniest thing that happened this weekend but ya once she got up the ppl saw us n they were just my neighbors looking at the house lol so it didnt really matter so we finished our picnic n then went home n then all of them went home n then i was really bored n i had to do my h/w  :(  n now im rele tired so im goin to go take a nap. 
                                                                *KARA* <3

Hey today i woke up on time for once! cuz i had to be at school at 730 cuz i had to sing in choir for chappel but i got there late cuz the stupid traffic uhgg! but ya so i got there n the whole choir was supposed to wear jeans n a black t-shirt n i asked emily if she would bring me one yesterday cuz i didnt have one n she said ya but she deffinatly wasnt there she got to school late so i was the only one in our choir (which there is like 50 of us) on stage singing with a bright red sweatshirt on n every1 else was wearin black lololol i stuck out so bad! but o well least i got to wear jeans the whole day. so then the rest of school was the same .. boring. i went to the movies tonight n it was really fun i hung out w/ jamie n kyle most of the time... n karley was there w/ sam n all them (but not chelsea :( ) so then we walked over to publix cuz the manager n the police were all bein gay n stuff n we saw chris n ricky n then saw rachael, brooke, n kalley n i was so happy to c them :) i love them so much! so we hung out w/ them for the rest of the time n then kyle just dissapeared somewhere lol like i didnt even notice when he left but o well so then brooke was pushing me n a grocery cart n she was goin super fast n scaring the poop out of me lol but ya it was really fun n ricky n chris had these hilarious batman masks on lol they were so funny. but ya this guy when we were all walkn to publix came running out of wendys yelling kara come back here right now n all this crap n i was like ok so me n brooke just ran away from him lol n he was like following all of us n then he just walked away so it was kinda weird :-/ lol but o well i think he was my moms friend but i have no idea but he knew my name so w/e he was scaring me tho cuz he looked really mad n stuff. but ya then we just all went in wendys n then my mom came n picked me n jamie up. tootles               
                                                     *Kara* <3

Hey! today was highlarious!! I went to school n of course woke up late like usual n i went to my classes like usual. but when i was in the hall n there is this gay black kid in 7th grade (well he isnt really gay but omg he really acts like it!) n so i said hi to him just to hear him talk cuz its really funny cuz he talks so gay n then i asked him wut his name was n then i told him mine n then the rest of the day he was like sayn hi to me every second! lol n then right before 4th period he came up to my locker n gave me a note n he was like here i made this for u! lol n it was so funny .. i mean it was nice but all i did was say hi to him n he was following me around lol. so i opened the note n it was some flowery drawing that he made for me lol n then there was a note n it n it said to kara n he gave me his # n then asked me for mine loolool n i really dont want him calling me sooo.... ya then after school he came up to me n asked me if i got his note n if i was goin to give him my # n i was um ok ya sure ... later lol (more like never) n jesse was standing behind sayn that he felt srry for me lol cuz like ya that kid is weird ( the gay one lol) then later i went to soccer n chelsea was so funny we were scrimaging these little 10 year olds n chelsea was slappin this one kids butt n blowin kisses at him n it was so funny haha! i love her to death! ya n richard (my coach) once again yelled at me for talkn to chelsea while we were scrimaging n omg he's really annoying he always yells at me n not chelsea n so i yelled at him back n i made him apologize lol. but ya he makes me really mad! but ya tomorrow i have to perform for choir for chappel so that should be fun.... i guess lol but at least we just get to wear a tshirt n jeans n not our usual formal black attire crap that we always have to wear. but ya i guess im goin to go cuz i got to be at school at 730 so tootles :-D           
                                                          *Kara* <3

Heeyy! this weekend was awesome! me n chelsea hung out the whole weekend. Friday she came over n we hung out for a few minutes n then got dropped off at wendy's to eat before we went to the movies. then we walked over to chickfila to go play n the little play thing but there was alot of lil kids n there n it was hot n smelly lol so then we walked over to Ross n the toy store(which is the coolest place ever) n then we walked over to the movies n nobody was there yet so we were kinda bored n then brooke, karley, sam, n billy showed up so we hung out w/ them. i tripped like 3 times in the movie n i was laughing really loud it was really funny. but anywho then we went home n just danced to techno like we always do which is so much fun! haha n we took my lil pink play tent from when i was lil n put it on my bed n slept in it. so then we woke up saturday n had a really yummy breakfeast n then went to beach soccer which we both really didnt want to go to but thats ok..... n then after that we went to some hotdog place n got food n then went bak to chelsea's house. then my mom picked us up n we went home. when we got home we wanted to ride our bikes to 7eleven so we put on my uniform shorts that the ppl sent me n they sent me HUGE SHORTS!  they were like below our knees n they looked ridiculous but it was so funny. so we got dressed in those n rode down to 7eleven n we looked really funny n then these guys started honking n yelling at us lololol it was so funny. and obviously they were just being funny cuz we looked really ugly lol. n we kept on trying to hide from these guys in the 7eleven cuz we were embarrassed lol. so then we rode bak to my house n went in the car w/ my sis to go pick up allie at some batmitzvah she was at n everybody there thought we were guys cuz we were still wearing those clothes lol but ok....n then allie came over n hung out w/ us n we went into this construction house across the street n we went on the roof n chelsea took a crap in the jonboy haha then we just hung out n then allie went home. then chelsea spent the night again n we woke up sunday morning n rode our bikes over to allie's house n hung out w/ her, kyle, n his friend nick n then went home to go eat our subway so we decided to eat it on top of the roof of the construction house across the street n we got ice n our subs n at it up there n it was really fun n then this truck pulled up at the house so we thought we were goin to be in trouble for being on the house so we grab all of our stuff n run out the bak lol n go hide n then we went home n watched lord of the rings until chelsea's mom came cuz we were super tired. n today was really boring n i have tons of h/w just like every day we have school so im goin to go now tootles!
